* 1177: Battle of Montgisard
* 1179: Battle of Banias
* 1179: Battle of Marj Ayyun
* 1179: Battle of Jacob&#x27;s Ford
* 1182: Battle of Belvoir Castle
* 1183: Battle of Al-Fule
* 1187: Battle of Hattin

