* &quot;In the Bleak Midwinter&quot; (on &quot;It&#x27;s A Cool Cool Christmas&quot; compilation) (did not chart)
* &quot;Come Home Billy Bird&quot;, the Divine Comedy (uncredited vocalist), No. 24 (w/b 28 March 2004)

